// THE VAULT DUO — breakout co-op level 2 (Insane mode).
//
// Conventions (shared by all breakout levels):
// - Entity names follow "brick_r{row}_c{col}" — the row digit drives the
//   score payout; keep names intact when editing.
// - Special bricks carry an EntityTag with '+'-joined tokens:
//     armored{N}      N total hits to destroy (2..=9)
//     drop_multiball  drops a multiball pickup when destroyed
//     drop_wrecking   drops a 10s wrecking-ball pickup
//     drop_insiculous drops a pickup granting BOTH effects
//   e.g. EntityTag(tag: "armored2+drop_wrecking"). No tag = plain brick.
// - Collider half-extents are absolute pixels; sprite size = scale x 80.
//   Keep in sync: scale (0.875, 0.3) <-> half_extents (35.0, 12.0).
// - Co-op layouts live in the MIDDLE band (y = +70 .. -70): both paddles
//   are in play, so shapes read well from above and below alike.
// - Prefabs are authoring sugar; the editor's save pipeline flattens them.

